Comment: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:18.26,CN - down,,0,0,0,,OP前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:23.56,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:26.06,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,去爸爸那裡
Comment: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:25.24,CN - down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:28.87,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這裡就是「爸爸的地方」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:31.71,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,能見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:35.71,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,能見到的 能見到的 能見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:36.96,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,能見到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:39.43,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,馬上就能見到恰噼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:44.10,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,還有爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:46.31,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.31,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:52.52,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:55.32,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:58.03,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,怎麼這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:58.99,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.70,CN - down,Satsuki,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:02.28,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,怎麼了五月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.58,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,很危險的 繪梨她還在睡覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.58,CN - up,Satsuki,0,0,0,,來這邊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.33,CN - up,Satsuki,0,0,0,,吶吶 和我玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:06.70,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:10.41,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,都說了這樣很危險啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:13.13,CN - up,Satsuki,0,0,0,,我不要 我要抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.13,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:18.34,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,爸爸 我是來見恰噼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:19.63,CN - up,Satsuki,0,0,0,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:20.51,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,恰噼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.72,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,聽 是恰噼的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:28.81,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,不是恰噼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:32.23,CN - down,Satsuki,0,0,0,,爸爸 這個女孩 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:33.69,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:36.98,CN - down,Satsuki,0,0,0,,為什麼她也叫你「爸爸」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.99,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,啊 啊 這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.37,CN - down,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,我也不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:04.84,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,也許是那兩個小孩吃掉了恰噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:10.10,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚噼不也會吃掉落蟬嗎 或許就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.10,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:15.48,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那麼 我們要把恰噼「取出來」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:16.31,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:18.61,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,要是調查過胃是否就能知道了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:20.99,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:30.83,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:36.04,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,給我能調查被捉住人類的胃的道具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:39.04,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我 我不知道啊噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.80,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這種道具沒有噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.72,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,欸 你說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:44.59,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:47.18,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那算了 我自己想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.59,CN - up,Takopi,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.97,CN - up,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香 別這樣噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:53.14,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,啊 用這個就能在夜晚進去而不被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:55.52,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香 你聽我說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.27,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.82,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.53,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:13.04,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我笨笨的 也很無能噼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:17.58,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,才會讓靜香你 努力到這麼身心俱殘的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:21.50,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,對不起 所以我們回家吧噼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:25.55,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,而且我能拿出讓你快樂遊玩的道具噼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.97,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,用「拍拍翅膀」稍微在空中懸浮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:34.35,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,用「變身調色盤」變成毛毛蟲 肯定也很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:38.56,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我希望你能變回原來的靜香噼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.32,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我只是 希望你能笑出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:42.57,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:47.33,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚噼也 不願幫助我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.37,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:50.37,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.58,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這雙眼好像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.66,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我曾在哪裡見過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.08,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.17,CN - up,Marina,0,0,0,,一直都是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:00.67,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,都說了 這很噁心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:03.88,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,快樂星人最為重要的「規則」被你破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.59,CN - up,Marina,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.59,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我明白噼 ***醬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.14,CN - up,Marina,0,0,0,,好討厭一個人 但從那時就一直這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:08.39,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,這是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.06,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,「罪」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.43,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.02,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.69,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,為什麼我會忘記呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.20,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.83,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,吶 那裡有什麼東西在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:35.29,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:36.79,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:43.29,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我是快樂星人 為大家帶來快樂噼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:47.34,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,首先我想知道噼 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.72,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,你的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:55.56,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.14,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,雲母坂麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.27,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我是快樂星人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:09.90,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,可以的話希望你能用「地球語言」給我起一個快樂名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:13.91,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,那就叫你「樂色廢物」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.91,CN - down,Student A,0,0,0,,看吧 那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:20.08,CN - down,Student B,0,0,0,,快看 她臉上的傷疤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.79,CN - down,Student A,0,0,0,,簡直就像黑幫一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:22.96,CN - down,Student C,0,0,0,,恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.09,CN - down,Student B,0,0,0,,聽說她一言不合就動手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.46,CN - down,Student D,0,0,0,,為什麼要戴著折耳根花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:28.71,CN - down,Student E,0,0,0,,但是稍微有點帥氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.47,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:33.43,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我想報答你請我吃的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.96,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這是我的快樂道具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:36.14,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.35,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,「花朵髮簪」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.93,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,用這個玩「扮花花」遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.11,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,誰要扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:45.98,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈 這個竟然是會發出土星兔聲音的原子筆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:51.57,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,喂 在家給我守點規矩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:59.45,CN - down,News anchor,0,0,0,,自前些日子起啟動的新冠病毒第十輪疫苗接種
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:03.46,CN - down,News anchor,0,0,0,,對於反覆接種的加強針 社會已然浮現出一些擔憂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:10.47,CN - up,News anchor,0,0,0,,雖然加強針是為了大幅降低重症化和住院風險而被政府推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:16.18,CN - up,News anchor,0,0,0,,但部分專家警告 這樣可能會伴隨一定的副作用而需警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.71,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.17,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.22,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.72,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,你起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.18,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,我以為你睡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.85,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,我現在就去準備晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:18.76,CN - up,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,我說 麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.43,CN - up,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,康普茶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:23.35,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,抱歉我回來這麼晚 今天發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:24.98,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,啊 康普茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.27,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,我明白了 現在給你倒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.28,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.07,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,藥 已經吃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:36.70,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,聽說它的副作用會做噩夢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:37.83,CN - up,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:41.20,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,那個 康普茶 康普茶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:44.71,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,抱歉 已經沒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:45.83,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:55.97,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,為 為什麼不在喝完前 在網路上提前訂一箱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:01.27,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,媽媽我只配喝這麼便宜的酒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:02.14,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:07.27,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,吶 媽媽需要的是用紅茶菌發酵的酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.94,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,麻里你也是這麼想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.32,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,媽媽 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.40,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,家務事一點也都做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:16.95,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,就是這樣才沒有男人願意追你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.70,CN - up,Marina,0,0,0,,對不起 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:21.12,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,你是 想說這一切都是我的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:26.75,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,連你也要說是因為我母乳太少才不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:29.21,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,才把孩子養得這麼失敗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:27.92,CN - up,Takopi,0,0,0,,好熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:32.55,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,玻 玻璃好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.51,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:38.59,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,小 小時候惹媽媽生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:41.43,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,玻 玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:45.60,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,這傷疤 就是被碎玻璃杯割爛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:48.90,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,玻 玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:49.98,CN - up,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.31,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:53.73,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,我想成為一位幸福的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:58.66,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,生下幸福的孩子 給予幸福的養育
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:09:59.70,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:02.41,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,這樣的話 媽媽她也一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.62,CN - up,Boy,0,0,0,,今天吃的點心 非常美味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:06.83,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 什麼嘛 你在「模仿」啊噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:04.45,CN - up,Mother,0,0,0,,挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:08.37,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,蛤 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:12.21,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我是說 麻里奈你每次都用力觸碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:14.96,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,是在模仿媽媽呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:19.84,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,人類就是這樣練習如何養育孩子的呀噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:24.10,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈肯定能成為一名優秀的媽媽噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:26.56,CN - up,Boy,0,0,0,,很危險的 要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:28.81,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,那麼 我來幫助你成為母親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.23,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:32.94,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,首先要選一位爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.82,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我們現在一起去找爸爸吧噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:38.70,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,哈 不用你多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:39.95,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,雲母坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:42.49,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:53.59,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,然後 在夏天 小學畢業後偶遇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:57.34,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,然後我們 不知不覺就開始交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:11:00.51,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,啊啦 這樣子啊 麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:03.60,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 要是早點告訴我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.22,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,嗯 所以今後我會介紹他給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.23,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,挺好的呀 我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:11.73,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,爸爸也因為新冠疫情工作並不順利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.98,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,我想他是時候回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.53,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,到那時候 我們再在一起吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:18.78,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:23.32,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,他是那家診所的兒子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.66,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,真期待他的未來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:28.29,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,啊 這件事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.21,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,繼承的是我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.88,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,盡量不要太提及就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:40.42,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,但是好久沒有和媽媽這麼開心地聊過天了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:41.76,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,是嗎噼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:47.14,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,真君會不會喜歡甜食呢 好像他喜歡鬆餅點心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.22,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,今後 做給他吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:50.77,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:55.69,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,傷疤的事 好像他也並不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:55.98,CN - up,Student A,0,0,0,,自言自語
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:57.40,CN - up,Student B,0,0,0,,慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:02.70,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,我 小時候發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.95,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,爸爸離家出走 媽媽也變化很大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:10.25,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,和我交好的朋友也沒有 一直都是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.08,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,但是最近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.33,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,快樂黏糊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:20.05,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:22.35,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,不過說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:26.26,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,要不是有你 我可能不會走到那條路上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:29.93,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,然後 就不會遇到直君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:34.60,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,所以 怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.07,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,最近稍微還不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:43.11,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.79,CN - down,Girl A,0,0,0,,聽說了嗎 有轉學生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:53.91,CN - down,Girl B,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:57.71,CN - down,Girl A,0,0,0,,說是超漂亮的人 應該是本地人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:13:00.46,CN - down,Girl B,0,0,0,,但是聽說以前發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:04.39,CN - down,Girl B,0,0,0,,還記得嗎 很多年之前的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:07.05,CN - down,Girl B,0,0,0,,她曾經自殺未遂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.35,CN - down,Girl A,0,0,0,,欸 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:17.31,CN - down,Girl B,0,0,0,,說是繩子中途斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:20.15,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,對不起 直君 你不喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.44,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,手 碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.65,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,欸 怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:36.25,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,久世同學除了我以外再無別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:40.79,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,一個人無依無靠單獨回到家鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.42,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我認為能再見到她就是奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.88,CN - up,Girl,0,0,0,,媽媽 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:46.63,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,小學的時候 我就被她所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.93,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,她只能依靠我了現在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:51.89,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我也明白自己非她莫屬了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:53.27,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.23,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:58.10,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,東君 還沒有來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.56,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,媽媽 好久沒有做這麼豐盛的晚餐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:03.48,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,還有麻里你喜歡的「巴伐露亞奶凍」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:08.20,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,好期待啊 不知道他會不會喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:12.12,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,快看 媽媽久違的吹了頭髮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:15.37,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 那我就去叫東君過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:17.50,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,等等我噼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:23.30,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,抱歉突然叫你出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:24.67,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.39,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,沒有什麼安排嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:33.01,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,除了東君我也沒有認識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:36.52,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,和我搭話的人也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:39.44,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,怎麼會 久世同學明明非常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:46.15,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,有 有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:53.62,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君才是沒關係吧 是不是挺忙的 和我不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:55.37,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:58.37,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:02.42,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,直君他 說今天不能來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:05.30,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,欸 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.72,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,不過 這也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:12.55,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,下次 吶 下次呢 下次什麼時候來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:18.59,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:24.19,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,這個 那個 我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.28,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.29,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,是我的不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:40.70,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,雲母坂她 肯定會受傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:44.30,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我總是半途而廢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.63,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,比起潤也 我也做不到他一樣好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:52.51,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,麻里 你做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.76,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,光沉默誰能知道你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:02.65,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,又是 那傷疤的原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:08.32,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,我真是「失職母親」啊 都怪我讓你變成殘缺品的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:08.95,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:11.51,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,但是 就因這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:14.40,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,我今天不也好好準備了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.95,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,還做了這麼多飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:23.83,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,直 直君 他喜歡別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.01,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:38.39,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,沒關係的 你不用和他人比較
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:42.85,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君的「事」我都看在眼裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:47.19,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,這樣一次又一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.27,CN - up,Marina,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:49.36,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,你肯定也瞧不起媽媽對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.36,CN - up,Marina,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:52.74,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,麻里你也不站在我這邊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.16,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,明明為了你做了那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:58.24,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,為什麼 麻里你也這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:04.29,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.50,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,難道是我的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.96,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,全部 全部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:15.00,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,全部 全部 全部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.55,CN - down,Marina's Mom,0,0,0,,都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:38.28,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,結果到最後還是沒和他說上話呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:46.21,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:51.38,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈 我回來啦噼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:56.13,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,抱歉噼 我沒能把東君帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:59.47,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,和他在一起的人感覺眼神很恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:03.68,CN - up,Marina,0,0,0,,對不起對不起對不起對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:03.68,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,好可怕噼 麻里奈你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:04.98,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.27,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:12.27,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,小學四年級的時候 就得把她殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.53,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,殺了久世靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:19.37,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,這樣的話 不僅是爸爸還有直君 都能在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:22.16,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:26.33,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,媽媽 不要丟下我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.79,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:37.38,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,為什麼啊 你還在這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.09,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:42.51,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,什麼啊 為什麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:49.65,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,要早知道是這樣就為你取個名字了 吶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:50.97,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:58.49,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,殺了她就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:02.53,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,小學四年級 久世靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:06.37,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,只要殺了她 就能讓你「快樂」了噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:09.83,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,用大快樂時鐘很簡單就能做到噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:13.13,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,交給我吧 等等我噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.17,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.11,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:33.77,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,果然要是給祂取個名字就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:37.78,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,章魚噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.32,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.41,CN - down,Happian A,0,0,0,,幫我摘下快樂果實噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:50.50,CN - down,Happian B,0,0,0,,來噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.50,CN - down,Happian A,0,0,0,,謝謝你噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.13,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,所以媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:20:00.88,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,用這個大快樂時鐘 回到小學四年級
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.43,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,把久世靜香殺了噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:11.10,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:12.85,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:16.39,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,若這是你的答案的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:17.90,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:21.61,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,我會消除你的全部記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:24.87,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,讓你回到剛出生時的快樂狀態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.79,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,你一個人 來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:33.33,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,破壞了快樂星球最為重要的「規則」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:36.96,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,不被允許再次返回這顆行星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:41.80,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,正因如此 你需要「重生」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:46.01,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,忘記一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:49.77,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這 這
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:53.23,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這樣子不行噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.06,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.10,CN - down,Happians,0,0,0,,欸 什麼噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.52,CN - up,Happians,0,0,0,,好恐怖噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:58.07,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:21:00.07,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,媽媽真是不講理噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:02.70,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.45,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,要去噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.95,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,但是你的記憶已經
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:12.50,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:20.84,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,汪愛凱夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.64,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,殺了是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:30.81,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,為什麼要這麼用力觸碰我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:34.85,CN - down,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,好好和我說話告訴我噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.40,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,沒事的噼 麻**醬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:44.95,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我一定會讓你快樂的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:48.16,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,就算失去記憶 我也一定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:54.07,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,**奈醬 **奈醬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:56.46,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:22:02.13,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我到底 要讓誰綻放笑容呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:12.22,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,為什麼我會忘記呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:15.59,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,要殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:20.69,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,要殺了久世靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:24.57,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,要殺了久世靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:27.32,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,要把她毀滅到魂飛魄散
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:29.41,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我全都想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:35.37,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,全部都是久世靜香的錯 麻里奈的爸爸 還有東君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:38.17,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,還有最重要的媽媽 都失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:40.79,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,要殺了她 要殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:42.46,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,久世靜香就惡魔一個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:43.71,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,要殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:44.67,CN - up,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊嘞 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:50.34,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,那個時候 麻里奈做了過分的事情 那難道不是壞的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:52.48,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,然後 我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.37,0:22:55.81,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,殺了麻里奈的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:22:57.10,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:22:59.52,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,你肚子餓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:05.03,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,午餐的麵包 要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:07.65,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,反正也吃不完
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:10.53,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:14.79,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,給我麵包的靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:18.08,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.38,0:23:24.75,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,你在這種地方做什麼 你個章魚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:29.72,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,東君
